data.description: Welcome to this story book ranch home in central Red Bluff!  Move in and enjoy the wonderful amenities, large covered patio looking out to the in-ground pool, established landscaped with so many beautiful plants and trees. Home offers a functional 3/1 floor plan with RV/boat parking and a 2 car garage.  This property has been so loved and cared for, roof is aprox 2 years old, interior has many updates and feels warm and inviting.  A must see.
